DETECTOR   (SIBAR) Four 300 um surface barrier detectors
           mounted in a 30 cm scattering chamber were used.
ERR-ANALYS Carbon build-up on the target introduced an uncertainty
           in the percentage of 13C in the target and resulted in
           an over-all error of approximately 50%
           (DATA-ERR) No information about source of uncertainty
